data.description: Better than new this stunning 4br 3ba home has an open floorplan with an office or formal dining, gas fireplace in the living room. Chef's eat in kitchen with gas cooktop, double ovens, pantry & large quartz island. Custom tiled laundry with folding station washer and dryer remain. Owner's suite on the main floor with large walk in closet. Primary bath has quartz counters, extra large custom tiled rain shower, led anti fog vanities, and tankless water heater. 2nd suite with walk in closet and full bath on the main floor. Bedrooms 3 & 4 ,bonus room and full bath upstairs along with 2 large walk in storage areas.  Covered patio with large privacy fenced backyard. Extra concrete pad for parking. All appliances remain.
